<h2><span><span><strong>Load Average含义</strong></span></span></h2>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; top命令中的Load Average显示的三个值表示在过去1分钟、5分钟、15分钟的系统负载。</span></p>
<h3 style="text-indent: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a name="_Toc254615870"></a>top命令中load average由来</span></h3>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; top命令直接从/proc/loadavg文件中读取值，没有做转换工作，该文件记录了系统在前1分钟、前5分钟和前15分钟的平均负载。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em>[root@linux_driver programming]# cat /proc/loadavg </em></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em>0.06 0.03 0.00 2/309 28525</em></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><em>[root@linux_driver programming]# </em></span></p>
<h3 style="text-indent: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a name="_Toc254615871"></a>负载的含义</span></h3>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 影响load average值大小的直接因素是系统中<strong><span style="color: red;">活动的进程数</span></strong>。Linux的系统负载指运行队列的平均长度，也就是等待CPU的平均进程数。活动的进程数可以很直观表明系统负载情况。值越大，表明CPU上<span style="color: blue;">正在运行和待运行的进程</span>数越多，也就是负载越大。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 系统中正在运行的进程越多，load average的值越大（等待CPU运行的进程队列越长）。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">Load Average越大，表明需要CPU干的活越多。</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: black;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
<h3 style="text-indent: 0cm;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><a name="_Toc254615872"></a>活动进程含义</span></h3>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 活动进程：处于<strong>TASK_RUNNING</strong>和<strong>TASK_UNINTERRUPTIBLE</strong>状态的进程。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; 进程的状态有以下7种。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>TASK_RUNNING</strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">进程处于运行（它是系统的当前进程）或者准备运行状态（它在等待系统将</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">CPU</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">分配给它）</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>TASK_INTERRUPTIBLE </strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">等待某个条件：中断、信号或能唤醒进程的资源</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>TASK_UNINTERRUPTIBLE </strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">处于睡眠状态，信号无法唤醒它。</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>TASK_STOPPED </strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">进程停止，当进程收到</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">SIGSTOP</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">、</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">SIGTSTP</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">、</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">SIGTTIN</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">或</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">SIGTTOU</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">信号时就会进入次状态</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>TASK_TRACED </strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">进程执行被调试器停止（调试程序使用</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">ptrace()</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">系统调用来监控程序）</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><strong>EXIT_ZOMBIE </strong></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">进程执行停止，但父进程还没调用</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">wait4</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">（）或</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">waitpid</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">（）来获取该进程返回信息。</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;" lang="EN-US">EXIT_DEAD </span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">进程的最终状态，父进程调用</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">wait4</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">（）或</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);" lang="EN-US">waitpid</span><span style="color: rgb(32, 32, 160);">（）来获取该进程返回信息，内核即将移除该进程。</span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""></span></p>
<h2 style="text-indent: 0cm;"><strong><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 255);"><a name="_Toc254615873"></a>Linux内核对load average的计算</span></strong></h2>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 内核通过下面的算式计算负载：</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;" lang="DE">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt; color: black;" lang="DE">load(t) = load(t-1) &nbsp;e<sup>-5/60R</sup> &nbsp;+ &nbsp;n(t) &nbsp;(1 – e<sup>-5/60R</sup>)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 11pt; color: black;" lang="DE">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><span style="font-size: 12pt; color: black;" lang="DE">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; n(t)是系统活动的进程数， R对应1、5、15分钟（如当计算15分钟的平均负载时，R的值就为15）。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Linux内核认为进程的生存时间服从参数为1的指数分布，指数分布的概率密度为：以内核计算负载load1为例，设相邻两个计算时刻之间系统活动的进程集合为S0。从1分钟前到当前计算时刻这段时间里面活动的load1个进程，设他们的集合是S1，内核认为的概率密度是:λe-λx，而在当前时刻活动的n个进程，设他们的集合是Sn内核认为的概率密度是1-λe-λx。其中 x = 5 / 60，因为相邻两个计算时刻之间进程所耗的CPU时间为5秒，而考虑的时间段是1分钟(60秒)。那么可以求出最近1分钟系统运行队列的长度：<br>
load1 <span style="color: white;"><br>
–&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;-</span>= |S1| <span style="color: white;">-</span>* λe-λx + |Sn| * (1-λe-λx) <span style="color: white;"><br>
–&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -</span>= load1 * λe-λx + n * (1-λe-λx)</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">其中λ = 1， x = 5 / 60， |S1|和|Sn|是集合元素的个数。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Linux内核定义一个unsigned long类型数组avenrun[3]，因为内核不能使用浮点数，就将低11位用于存放负载的小数部分，高21位用于存放整数部分。</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; avenrun[0]</span>对应前1分钟系统负载；</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; avenrun[1]</span>对应前5分钟系统负载；</span></p>
<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 11pt; line-height: 150%;" lang="EN-US">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; avenrun[2]</span>对应前15分钟系统负载；</span></p>
<p class="a" style="text-indent: 21pt;"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">内核<strong><span style="color: blue;">每隔</span></strong><strong><span style="color: blue;" lang="EN-US">5</span></strong><strong><span style="color: blue;">秒钟</span></strong>更新一次load average的值。<strong></strong></span></p>

<p class="a"><span style="font-family: tahoma,arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; R对应1、5、15分钟（如当计算15分钟的平均负载时，R的值就为15）。</span></p>
